name: Only I know the reincarnation world of the plot
summary: "Big news, Bucky the Clown is as powerful as Whitebeard!""The Gold Saint actually lost to a Bronze one?!""Hero Association, don't worry about heroes below S level!""The ultimate BOSS in the Naruto world is named Payne!"The anime I once loved has now turned into a dangerous world, and Fang Bo, as a reincarnator, must struggle to survive in it.It was true originally, but why did he think everyone was a little strange?When he saw a group of reincarnations preparing to surround and kill Saitama, he finally realized that he was the only one who knew the plot.
author: Wan_Ju_Ren
